Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.92,0:00:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亚少年  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.08,0:00:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有两个力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.24,0:00:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个是Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.87,0:00:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对任何对手都能下令使其绝对服从的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个是黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:18.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为破坏父亲统治的布里塔尼亚的他自己的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.03,0:00:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修借ZERO这个代号行动起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.18,0:00:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了替母亲报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.23,0:00:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有为了创造妹妹娜娜莉能幸福生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这行动会导致怎样的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在谁也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 12
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}京都来的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于总督的作战  日本解放战线几乎是毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃亡中的成员也接连被抓获
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是揶揄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我军正苦恼着如何重新振作的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我并没有这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.57,0:02:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实难道不是占领后的政策有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11区的地下铁路网  矿山  矿道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么就这么放置着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平民区的户籍管理和地产的所有权还是这么的暧昧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府势力的温床就这么被放置着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  地下铁几乎是遍布全国
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理想要覆盖到租界以外的地方的话  预算实在是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使明白这会成为恐怖分子的据点和逃跑路线还这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:54.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是克洛维斯殿下的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:02:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  太过强硬会造成内乱状态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会给中华联邦可趁之机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是已经给了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的势力正在慢慢集结力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事务次官
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在内政省的管理下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有对这个地区进行自治的11区的代表是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为NAC的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前几天的作战中抓住了NAC的把柄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但资料被掩埋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有嫌疑是毫无疑问的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要控制住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  名门和财阀的集合体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是历史的遗物了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.39,0:03:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只不过是传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有证据
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果压制了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无法恢复11区的经济
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对本国的征税也会有影响
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:51.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且编号住民自己照顾自己是帝国的大方针
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么黑色骑士团的搜索呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从留下的挖掘机械资料来看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然证明成田的事是ZERO的所为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但找不到团员尸骸以外的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能对京都出手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又无法把ZERO逼入绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从结果上来看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的无能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到布里塔尼亚的皇女竟能做到如此地步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放战线已经分裂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本统一的力量之灯火已经消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说还太早
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说还在逃亡中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但藤堂还健在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说连无赖·改也失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有希望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色骑士团吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莲二式也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木朱雀救出事件以来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您对ZERO很热衷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于特拉法尔加战役的败北
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[1805年,在纳尔逊指挥下的英国舰队于直布罗陀海峡西北的特拉\N法尔加角击败法国和西班牙联合舰队的海战。挫败了拿破仑登陆\N英国本土的作战计划。英国掌握了制海权，纳尔逊战死。]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊丽莎白三世被革命势力包围在爱丁堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}当时布里塔尼亚公镇守在殖民地美洲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}也就是我们现在的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  一脸复杂的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便秘？ 宿醉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么是鲁路修不在  感到寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  卡莲也一起缺席  又是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真悠闲啊  世界却正为前几天的成田事件而混乱不已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀也因为这事今天请假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我只是觉得鲁鲁和卡莲的事更成问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是喜欢你的这种性格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别拿我寻开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说  你直说不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不行的  这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  如果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拒绝了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定连朋友也做不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也用不着  笑得那么夸张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很开心啊  在这个地方  还有我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还是做好一点觉悟的好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不变的事物在哪儿都是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  别这么认真嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果无论如何都想知道的话  干脆去问本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那边情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁…鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不是休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉稍微有点发烧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnDFPHSGothic-W5\fe128\fs25\b1\alpha&H15&}咲{\r}世子白天有点事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小娜娜的情况好点了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长  那个文件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分发到各学年的各个班级上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这么会差遣人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有能干的部下真是幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部下？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  还真是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  会长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样对心脏不好啊  你那种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  门票
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:09.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些文件里有没有混进我的信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡乱猜测
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说那家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.75,0:07:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:07:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没说不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:08:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一起去听音乐会而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是这样而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  是机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都表扬我们很好地使用了红莲二式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是感动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是被那个白色铠甲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平手嘛  平手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙莉那家伙怎么了  那么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸是去单身赴任
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是说要让我心情好一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以总是会送这种东西给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.27,0:08:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙不吃玩笑这一套
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉城笑得太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都来的诏书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说务必要和我们见面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是需要那么大惊小怪的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说大惊小怪  那可是京都啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果让他们承认的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也会提供我们资金援助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们拮据的财政也会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财政
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果按我计划的预算的话应该没问题才对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经是大组织了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人数增加了可是预料之外的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好教导新人陪他们到处玩也是预料之外？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之  会计的工作就交给扇了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从以前开始钱物管理就是交给我来做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想让人信任的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就给出相应的成果来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你居然说我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种说我们是同伴  还不给我们看脸的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底打算怎么样啊  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  这个么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的真面目到底是什么不是问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO有让那个科奈莉娅防不胜防的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们黑色骑士团的首领啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你说还需要其他什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妮娜…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你身体不舒服的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我们本来是直人的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妹妹卡莲都不介意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为作为首领二代的你把位子让给他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在成田的时候大家也
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那几乎可以说是胁迫了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们这些干部也保密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能性的12个人已经掌握了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就是如何出牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是需要即兴发挥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:49.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才说了多管闲事的话  实在是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲  你也想知道我的真实面目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人  知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我告退了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧好像已经退了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能只是想任性一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任性？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近总感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥好像要去很远的地方似的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以身体可能自然地配合了一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.36,0:11:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总会在你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我可以说任性的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请再握着我的手一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样就睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得会再看见那个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要拜托我事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照你给我的提示行动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论京都那边的意图为何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都想要得到那些人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这是为了你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你生存的目的是需要的话  我可以帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C.  我需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  这是你忘了的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不知道什么时候才能回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算给她打拒绝的电话而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要遵守约定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  正好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于今天的约定  我说不定会迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  肯定没有问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京中央单轨铁路线  至成田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把其他的干部也带来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人是这么吩咐的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让他们警戒周围的情况了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.41,0:13:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就叫他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏较严重的尸体请送到第二帐篷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有遗物的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽快确认主人身份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已确认身份的请送到第一帐篷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并书面登记发现场所  时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二医疗班很快就会来帮忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的在吗  她  在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料里她也不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经满足了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸体发掘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:14:00.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话  我还是希望继续帮忙救援
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在你死心之前请自便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.79,0:14:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且也算是科奈莉娅殿下的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO…黑色骑士团到底想要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们认为建筑在这牺牲之上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能完成什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是正义的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用本人的话来说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是正义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会想说『正义是什么』这种让人害臊的理论吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们姑且是军人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源包的更换
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.95,0:14:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞希尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:50.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我调查过了  纯血派他们的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  是辐射波动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到居然协助敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个拉克夏塔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的机师也是王牌级的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀精神不稳定的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再次和这种对手战斗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想说赢不了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经过了很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:18.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是冷静一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上升
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你们带来不便了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.52,0:15:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人在等大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里  富士矿山
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能到这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不会有错的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座山  这个形状
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说  这个下面有sakuradite
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诱发战争的罪魁祸首
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有入侵者  毫不迟疑就会被射杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到居然把势力延伸到这种地方来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都果然厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很丑恶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去曾经如此山清水秀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以水清澈  山碧绿的富饶而著称的灵峰富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.42,0:16:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如同现在已屈服在帝国之下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽仍生存但被不断凌辱的我们日本的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人哀叹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为无法以真面目见你们而道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是ZERO  关于这点你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能不看透
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看吧  你的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO赐予了我们力量与胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫扇的是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:16:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:16:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把ZERO的假面拿下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也想相信  对你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:15.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  请让我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女…女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人不是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和ZERO在一起的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你  不是日本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES  京都的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐原泰藏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让知道大人真面目的人活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不用说她不是日本人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:46.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是软弱啊  而且
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:17:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行为和思想都很陈腐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  你们才赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被远隔操作射击到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗  谁也不要动手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐原泰藏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且不论和sakuradite挖掘产业有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为桐原产业的创建者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木政权的影之建立者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  战败后摇身一变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积极地成为殖民地的协助者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通称  卖国贼的桐原
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  他的真正身份
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是管理全国反抗者们的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都六家的重镇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城府真深
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不一般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  对大人的诽谤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如您所猜测的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  不是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得不能让我们看到脸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然不是日本人  为什么要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:18:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有什么企图
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:01.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亚的崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道能够实现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.86,0:19:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果问为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有不得不完成这事的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是对手实在是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐原公
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八年前被送到那家当牺牲品的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.99,0:19:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时无论如何承蒙照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果对手不是我的话你是不是打算把他当作人质
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于我来说  只能做到提出我的愿望而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八年前的种子开花了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死  看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人毫无疑问是布里塔尼亚的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法显示真正的面目我也能够理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能够保证
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟随ZERO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据点隐蔽或者情报搜寻这些我们也会协助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  桐原公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要踏上去吗  修罗之路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果  这是我的命运的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第2  第5  第7  第8  第9小队
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在管理总部的指挥下继续独自作业
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲奈特之后是这儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗骸是那具
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  因为是这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么请您确认
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.85,0:20:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然已经不在了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样从现在开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.93,0:21:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色骑士团真正成为如我所愿而行动的组织了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:11.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  对不起我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你已经走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  先不管那些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之先找个避雨的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO是弱者的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.06,0:21:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.27,0:21:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  为什么杀了我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.78,0:21:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.47,0:21:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都从没有打过我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:43.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么坏事都没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  被活埋了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法呼吸的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.17,0:21:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么爸爸要死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.62,0:21:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.97,0:21:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.79,0:22:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你  鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.33,0:23:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.77,0:23:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动的结果这种
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.55,0:23:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.54,0:23:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.22,0:23:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从舞台上消失很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.20,0:23:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要舍弃ZERO这个存在就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.30,0:24:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要堵住桐原的嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.91,0:24:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能恢复鲁路修·兰佩洛奇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  可是
